{"title":"致吴王等君","date":"1957-6-0","authors":["中央民族学院","杨振常"],"contents":[{"text":"致吴王等君","type":"title"},{"text":["中央民族学院","杨振常"],"type":"authors"},{"text":"（杨振常：中央民族学院历史系民族学研究班学生,“蜜蜂社”成员）","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(一)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"口说助整风，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"别有幽衷。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“民主党派联合会”，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"信口雌黄谈“监督”，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"胡说一通。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"王吴相呼应，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"异曲同工。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"千言婉转无人从。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"万千心事竟落空，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"君何自容。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"(二)","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"借鸣放机会，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"作浪兴波。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“肃反斗争不道德”，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"“八年毛病何其多”，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"其意云何？","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"此语不能解，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"旧调重谈。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"底事揭穿运回戈。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"人民天下君不惯，","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"心在何边。","type":"paragraph"},{"text":" 蜜蜂","type":"paragraph"},{"text":"来源：《关于“野草”、“蜜蜂”社反动小集团的材料》，中共中央民族学院整风办公室编，1957年12月。","type":"appellation"}]}